OL,3,CLottery winners give back to hospital
OL,4,Cthat saved son's life
OL,6,F"The hospital does so much incredible
OL,7,Fwork and I am truly honoured ` thanks
OL,8,Fto my National Lottery win ` to be
OL,9,Fback here today giving something back
OL,10,Fin terms of my time and contributing
OL,11,Fto a project which really will benefit
OL,12,Fthousands of people for many years to
OL,13,Fcome."
OL,15,FThe group of winners, worth a combined
OL,16,Ftotal of #32 million, spent the day
OL,17,Fplanting borders alongside a new
OL,18,Fwalkway around the Alder Centre
OL,19,Fbereavement unit.
