OL,6,FThe hospital is currently undergoing
OL,7,Fmulti-million-pound redevelopment to
OL,8,Fcreate a world-class healthcare
OL,9,Fcampus, where all aspects of
OL,10,Fchildren's health can be addressed in
OL,11,Fone dedicated space.
OL,13,FPatricia Gill from Warrington, who
OL,14,Fwith husband John won #1 million on
OL,15,FEuromillions in 2015, said: "It is
OL,16,Fwonderful to think we can play a part
OL,17,Fin such a major building project and
OL,18,Fat such a prestigious location ` not
OL,19,Fonly in the UK ` but across Europe.
