OL,3,CLottery winners give back to hospital
OL,4,Cthat saved son's life
OL,6,F"Everyone knows about Alder Hey and
OL,7,Fthe tremendous life-saving work that
OL,8,Fthe hospital does and to be able to
OL,9,Fhelp to create an even better
OL,10,Fenvironment for children and their
OL,11,Ffamilies, really is a true honour!"
OL,13,FFiona Ashcroft, chief executive at
OL,14,FAlder Hey Children's Charity, said:
OL,15,F"We have been extremely grateful to
OL,16,Fhave the lottery winners on site `
OL,17,Fthey have certainly done an excellent
OL,18,Fjob and played a very important part
OL,19,Fin developing our Children's Health
OL,20,FCampus here at Alder Hey."
